### Steps to reproduce

1. Create a HingeJoint3D node (or any 3D Joint) and set it's Node_A and Node_B to separate RigidBody3D nodes.
2. Toggle the HingeJoint3D node's visibility or any of its parent node's visibility in the scene editor.
3. The HingeJoint3D Gizmo is always drawn regardless of visibility.

### Minimal reproduction project (MRP)

The aformentioned step to reproduce are trivial and should suffice.

